{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":87,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_hou_xi_bai","speaker_name":"侯希白","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"小弟就送子陵至此为止，子陵只须向船上乌江帮的人报上名字，便不用理会其他，小弟已给足船费，一切均安排妥当。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":5,"line_end":7},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_hou_xi_bai","text":"乌江帮为何这么大面子？","tone":"疑问","chapter":305,"line_start":9,"line_end":9},{"speaker":"char_hou_xi_bai","speaker_name":"侯希白","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"乌江帮的沙老大经营三峡客货运送生意足有十多年的历史，信誉昭着，因其与巴陵帮一向关系良好，又为萧铣负责在巴蜀买粮后付运等事宜，所以很吃得开。子陵可以放心。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":11,"line_end":13},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_hou_xi_bai","text":"原来如此，难怪这么大的一条船，只有那么二、三十个乘客，该是以运货为主，载客只是兼营吧？","tone":"疑问","chapter":305,"line_start":15,"line_end":17},{"speaker":"char_hou_xi_bai","speaker_name":"侯希白","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"但真正赚钱的却是客运生意，船资看情势随时调整，由于舱房只有十五间，想弄个床铺不是有钱便办得到，我是找上沙老大说话，才为子陵办妥此事的。","tone":"大笑","chapter":305,"line_start":19,"line_end":21},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_hou_xi_bai","text":"多谢侯兄的安排，小弟要起行哩！","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":23,"line_end":23},{"speaker":"char_hou_xi_bai","speaker_name":"侯希白","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"若非小弟要竟地潜修，钻研不死印卷上的心法，定要陪子陵畅游三峡，子陵珍重。","tone":"温柔","chapter":305,"line_start":25,"line_end":27},{"speaker":"char_wu_jiang_bang_da_han","speaker_name":"乌江帮大汉","listener":null,"text":"头儿！弓爷来啦！","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":49,"line_end":51},{"speaker":"char_lin_lang","speaker_name":"林朗","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"弓爷你老人家好，小人林朗，乃乌江帮梅花堂香主，沙老大吩咐下来，对弓爷的招待绝不可怠慢，请这边来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":57,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"小杰","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"伯伯抱抱，杰儿要看。","tone":"恳求","chapter":305,"line_start":153,"line_end":153},{"speaker":"char_xiao_jie_ma","speaker_name":"小媳妇","listener":"char_xiao_jie","text":"杰儿！你怎么不听话，烦扰这位大叔哩！","tone":"认真","chapter":305,"line_start":171,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_xiao_jie_ma","speaker_name":"小媳妇","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"不好意思，劣儿烦着大叔哩！","tone":"温柔","chapter":305,"line_start":175,"line_end":177},{"speaker":"char_gong_chen_chun","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_xiao_jie_ma","text":"没关系！","tone":"温柔","chapter":305,"line_start":179,"line_end":179}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xu_zi_ling","name":"徐子陵","alias":["弓辰春","疤脸客"],"identity":"扬州双龙之一，化名弓辰春","faction":"无","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"扬州双龙之一，武功高强，化名弓辰春乘船离开巴蜀","personality":{"traits":["重情重义","低调内敛","机敏果决","心地善良","思虑深远"],"speech_style":"温和有礼，言简意赅","temperament":"沉稳冷静"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"挚友","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"自幼相伴的兄弟"},{"target":"char_hou_xi_bai","type":"挚友","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"相互尊重的朋友"},{"target":"char_shi_qing_xuan","type":"恋人","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"情感复杂"},{"target":"char_shi_fei_xuan","type":"恋人","intensity":75,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"若即若离"}],"known_skills":["skill_jiuyin_zhenjing","skill_changsheng_zuqin","skill_buxiang_ji","skill_poxie_danfa"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[305],"source_refs":[{"chapter":305,"line_start":3,"line_end":3,"text":"徐子陵仍是\"疤脸客\"弓辰春的样貌身份"}]},{"id":"char_hou_xi_bai","name":"侯希白","alias":[],"identity":"多情公子，花间派传人","faction":"花间派","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"花间派传人，多情才子，送徐子陵登船后独自潜修","personality":{"traits":["风流倜傥","才情出众","重情重义","潇洒不羁","心思细腻"],"speech_style":"文雅有礼，语气轻松","temperament":"随性洒脱"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xu_zi_ling","type":"挚友","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"相互尊重"},{"target":"char_shi_fei_xuan","type":"恋人","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"曾经倾慕"}],"known_skills":["skill_huajian_pai"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[305],"source_refs":[{"chapter":305,"line_start":5,"line_end":27,"text":"侯希白送别徐子陵"}]},{"id":"char_lin_lang","name":"林朗","alias":[],"