{"segment":2,"line_start":88,"line_end":182,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lin_lang","speaker_name":"林朗","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"正午时份，我们会经过巴郡，由巴郡到巴东那段水路更是险要，如若顺风，明天黄昏可抵郑郡，逗留一晚，那里寺庙众多，弓爷若有兴趣，可到城内走走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":113,"line_end":115},{"speaker":"char_gong_chen_chun","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_lin_lang","text":"甚么时候才可入峡？","tone":"疑问","chapter":305,"line_start":117,"line_end":117},{"speaker":"char_lin_lang","speaker_name":"林朗","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"过白帝城后个许时辰就是峡口，我们看惯的可没甚么，若弓爷是初次游峡，那种山峰夹江耸崎的险峻形势，确可今弓爷叹为观止的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":119,"line_end":121},{"speaker":"char_gong_chen_chun","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_lin_lang","text":"未入峡景色已这么壮观，入峡后当然是更有看头。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":125,"line_end":127},{"speaker":"char_lin_lang","speaker_name":"林朗","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"昨晚追着来要我们停船的人，弓爷是否认识？","tone":"疑问","chapter":305,"line_start":129,"line_end":131},{"speaker":"char_gong_chen_chun","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_lin_lang","text":"该与我没有关系，林香主知否他们是何方神圣？","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":133,"line_end":135},{"speaker":"char_lin_lang","speaker_name":"林朗","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"小人就是弄不清楚他们的身份，才顺口问弓爷一声。这么看可能是与船上其他客人有关，弓爷不必放在心上。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":137,"line_end":141},{"speaker":"char_gong_chen_chun","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_xiao_jie","text":"小孩子怎可在船上乱闯？","tone":"担心","chapter":305,"line_start":149,"line_end":151},{"speaker":"char_gong_chen_chun","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_xiao_jie","text":"看到吗？","tone":"温柔","chapter":305,"line_start":157,"line_end":159}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_kou_zhong","name":"寇仲","alias":[],"identity":"扬州双龙之一","faction":"无","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"扬州双龙之一，在山中迷路，前往寻找宋玉致","personality":{"traits":["豪迈不羁","重情重义","机智果敢","勇猛无畏","风趣幽默"],"speech_style":"豪爽直接","temperament":"热情冲动"},"relationships":[{"target":"c