{"segment":3,"line_start":183,"line_end":251,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"有没有人懂汉语，我只是途经问路吧！","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":199,"line_end":201},{"speaker":"char_song_yu_zhi","speaker_name":"宋玉致","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"寇仲！你到这里来干甚么？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":305,"line_start":209,"line_end":211},{"speaker":"char_gong_chen_chun","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_han_ze_nan","text":"甚么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":305,"line_start":217,"line_end":217},{"speaker":"char_lin_lang","speaker_name":"林朗","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"弓爷你来评评理，这艘船说好是到九江去的，走甚么路线泊那几个码头，都早定下，怎可随便更改。这位韩泽南先生总不明白。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":221,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_han_ze_nan","speaker_name":"韩泽南","listener":"char_lin_lang","text":"在下非是不明白，只是求林大哥行个方便，让我们在巴陵下船而已！","tone":"恳求","chapter":305,"line_start":225,"line_end":227},{"speaker":"char_lin_lang","speaker_name":"林朗","listener":"char_han_ze_nan","text":"还要我说多少遍，巴陵是长江联的地头，我们乌江帮最近和他们有些争执，这么忽然泊岸，会有麻烦的。","tone":"淡然","chapter":305,"line_start":229,"line_end":231},{"speaker":"char_gong_chen_chun","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_han_ze_nan","text":"让我来劝劝韩兄好了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":241,"line_end":241},{"speaker":"char_lin_lang","speaker_name":"林朗","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"弓爷果然是明白人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":243,"line_end":243},{"speaker":"char_gong_chen_chun","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_han_ze_nan","text":"韩兄可否借一步说话？","tone":"陈述","chapter":305,"line_start":247,"line_end":247},{"speaker":"char_han_ze_nan","speaker_name":"韩泽南","listener":"char_gong_chen_chun","text":"有甚么好说的。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":305,"line_start":249,"line_end":249}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_han_ze_nan","name":"韩泽南","alias":[],"identity":"读书人，携妻儿乘船","faction":"无","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"读书人，携妻儿乘乌江帮客船，似惹上麻烦急于在巴陵下船","personality":{"traits":["书生气重","忧心忡忡","爱护家人","固执己见","胆小怕事"],"speech_style":"文雅书生气","temperament":"焦虑"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_jie_ma","type":"恋人","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"夫妻"},{"target":"char_xiao_jie","type":"亲属","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"父子"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[305],"source_refs":[{"chapter":305,"line_start":223,"line_end":227,"text":"这位韩泽南先生总不明白。在下非是不明白，只是求林大哥行个方便"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_li_liao_cun_zhai","name":"俚僚村寨","region":"岭南山区","one_line":"深山中的俚僚族村寨，吊脚楼建筑，风景清幽","source_refs":[{"chapter":305,"line_start":183,"line_end":192,"text":"一道河流从西北流来，蜿蜓穿过村寨中心"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
